---
title: Chicken Satay Noodle Toss with Carrot Ribbons & Peanuts
description: If you were to ask us, one weekly stir-fry night is mandatory. So is a pasta night. So if you’re looking to kill two birds with one stone, so to speak, our chefs have got just the dish for you. You’ll make your own chicken satay with a spicy coconut-based peanut sauce. Mix that up with carrots, scallion, and ramen noodles and you’re ready for stir-fry night.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-satay-noodle-toss-d43a35aa.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/chicken-satay-noodle-toss-61670cfc4a8951755d18b6ea-9d59472b.pdf
